{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6a9f544dea","title":"粤汉铁路工人致朱先生","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40baae63f7","index":0,"year":1922,"month":9,"day":10,"articleId":"6a9f544dea"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji2","name":"毛泽东全集第2卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8afd3011d4","type":"paragraph","text":"粤汉铁路工人致朱先生","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6a9f544dea"},{"id":"5e34de7e31","type":"paragraph","text":"（1922年9月10日）朱先生伟鉴：工等此次要工，出于方不得已，全因痛苦太深。务员肆虑，待遇不良，详情工等向数路王局长及洋总管所提出各条件。半月以来，甘心忍痛，无如王局长有意迁延，张苗未去，所请不允全路惯激，追而出此。先生有意维持，易胜感谢！催散路向重，有系统管理，负责任者，自有当局。幸先生迅向徐家棚王局长及洋总管交涉，朝允八条，夕即开车，决不违命。再工等颜有团体组织，此次姜工系由全路俱乐部联合会，负完全交涉责任。特并奉闻。即颂勋祺！诸维灵照不尽！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6a9f544dea"}],"page":{"id":"f8ab84d146","publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"6a9f544dea","start":494,"end":494}}}},"__N_SSG":true}